00:13:48,736 --> 00:13:50,741
<i>Am I the only one
who just got chills?</i>

358
00:13:50,825 --> 00:13:53,276
Let's start with the
business deductions

359
00:13:53,361 --> 00:13:56,034
from Schedule A on the
tax return dated

